scene_description_enriched: The image depicts a centaur, a mythical creature with the torso and head of a human and the body of a horse, aiming a bow and arrow. The centaur has curly brown hair and a beard, and its human torso is bare. The horse body is dark brown. The background is a landscape with rolling green hills and a blue sky. The scene is framed by a decorative border. The text above the image, "Sagittarie", identifies the centaur as the astrological sign Sagittarius.
